## LogLevel enum

Possible levels to log in the console.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare enum LogLevel 
```

## Enumeration Members

|  Member | Value | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  Debug | <code>4</code> | Debug, info, warnings, and errors will be shown in the console. |
|  Error | <code>1</code> | Only errors will be shown in the console. |
|  Info | <code>3</code> | Only info, warnings, and errors will be shown in the console. |
|  Silent | <code>0</code> | No logs will be shown in the console. |
|  Verbose | <code>5</code> | All logs will be shown in the console. |
|  Warn | <code>2</code> | Only warnings and errors will be shown in the console. |
